Ayten Amer (amụrụ Samar Ahmed Abd El Ghaffar Amer, 22 Nọvemba 1981, Alexandria, Egypt) bụ onye Egypt na-eme ihe nkiri.
Amer kwagara Cairo mgbe ọ dị afọ anọ
O mechara mụọ ime ihe nkiri na iduzi ma rụọ ọrụ dị ka onye nlereanya, nke nyeere ya aka imeri egwu ya maka igwefoto
Ọrụ mbụ ya bụ na Hadret El Motaham Aby (Mr
Guilty is My Father), ya na Nour El Sherif.
Amer bụ nwanne nwanyị onye na-eme ihe nkiri bụ Wafaa Amer, ma nwee otu nwa nwanyị, Ayten Ezzelarab.
